(1) A lot of people hang out here while they are at work.  Some of these people work at places where incoming files can be (and are) monitored.  There are files (esp images) that would be considered taboo in these situations, even though they did not actually go lOOKING for them.  THEREFORE... no porn allowed.  Link to is allowable, aslong as there is a warning, but ... NO Porn directly posted.  Do and it will be removed, continue and YOU will be removed.<br>
That would be my first rule contribution.<br>
<br>
(2) Spamming is a pain in the ass.  It sucks up bandwidth and creates useless posts which, as you zoom through a long string of them, can cause you to loose actual posts that have merit and meaning.  Rule - no spamming.  If you are OBVIOUSLY doing it, you should be removed, but if it is questionable intent, I would like to see at least one warning before removal.<br>
<br>
That's it.  The end.  I see no reason for any more rules in THIS particular section.  I understand your claim about threats IRL, but since this is a digital medium, that is hard to determine for sure.  I say, threaten all you want.  If you think you want to kick my ass and run over me with your VW Rabbit, go ahead and post it.  <br>
Of course, I am going to take you about as seriously as I take GW, but I see no reason why you can't post it.  Why should I worry?  The grand majority of you don't know who I am or a single damn thing about me.  Do you REALLY think I am going to take anything you say seriously?  And if you DO want to kill me, and you DO know who I am... then please do post here ... in the open forum.  That way, I have evidence that it was premeditated AND I know to keep an eye out for you.  <br>
Conclusion ... For this forum, the fewer rules we have, the better.  I only see reason for two rules, and those two ONLY becasue not having them would hurt the board.  I realize that this would drive Wrin to a fit of insanity as she runs screaming about our lack of order and supression, but would we expect anything less? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kwipdapimp>kwip dapimp</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 220<br> <font color=#330000>(11/19/03 11:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1142.topic&index=107>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rules Discussion</span><hr size=1> if i met wrin IRl id stab her boobie with a bic.<br>
